Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:54.74,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}啊 直到天空那遥远的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:59.67,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}そう　翔てゆくような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:59.67,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}像这样飞翔
